{"word":"πλέγμα","slug":"πλέγμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλέγμα</b></el> <el>(πλέγμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πλέκω'><el>πλέκω</el></a>\n<p/><i>plaited work, wicker-work</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>wreaths, braids</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}